**View Provider:Component ka meta data hai.
1.iska use hum jb krte hai jb hum class ko component lavel ka krdete hai.
2.Class ko component lavel ka bnanae kai liye class ko View Provider mai rkhte hai.
3.Hum class ko @module lavel ki bhi btanskte hia but yai good prectice nhi hai kyoki jb bhi modula load hoga vo classbhi load ho jayegi
chahe uska use ho ya na ho. isliye class ko componet lavel ka bnate hai kyoki jb bhi componelt load hoga vo class tbhi call hogi. jisse 
Angular apication prformation pr koi iffect nhi pdta hai.

4.Hum class ko component mai bhi directly bna skte hai
